The package boost-statechart is compatible with built-in CMake targets of FindBoost.cmake:

    find_package(Boost REQUIRED COMPONENTS statechart)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::statechart)

or the generated cmake configs via:

    find_package(boost_statechart REQUIRED CONFIG)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE Boost::statechart)
